name: Capitalist intimidation
description: Imperialism as a form of monopoly in the capitalist economic system, imperialism is said to be an effort to forcefully expand the territory of one country by carrying out territorial conquests which are the basis for establishing political and economic domination over other countries that are not colonies. What are the impacts? micro businesses will die one by one, superior products in the country will be lost and flooded with products from outside, opportunities of creative human will be lost and defeated by corporate and capitalist interests, this painting is a rejection and satire of capitalist actors.
